Description:

As a result of hitting the $3,500 stretch goal of my Kickstarter campaign (check it out here if you haven't yet: http://kck.st/1BGtBQ6), I'm releasing "Pandora" as a free download for you all to enjoy!

Hugely inspired by the Borderlands video game franchise, Pandora is a classic MDK track that spans a few different genres in a few short minutes.
